				<p class="postmetadata">24.06.2014 (Norbert Rost) Kategorie: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/die-kleinen-schritte/" title="Alle Beiträge in Die kleinen Schritte ansehen" rel="category tag">Die kleinen Schritte</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/presseschau/" title="Alle Beiträge in Presseschau ansehen" rel="category tag">Presseschau</a>  &middot; Tags: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/berlin/" rel="tag">Berlin</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/bielefeld/" rel="tag">Bielefeld</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/degrowth/" rel="tag">Degrowth</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/dresden-auf-entzug/" rel="tag">Dresden auf Entzug</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/leipzig/" rel="tag">Leipzig</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/lesertreffen/" rel="tag">Lesertreffen</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/rob-hopkins/" rel="tag">Rob Hopkins</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/transition/" rel="tag">Transition</a>  &middot; <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/2014/06/rob-hopkins-berlin-degrowth-leipzig-lesertreffen/#comments" title="Kommentiere Rob Hopkins in Berlin+Bielefeld, Degrowth in Leipzig: Lesertreffen">19 Kommentare &#187;</a> </p>

